text: Moni Kangana Dutta (born September 13) is an Indian supermodel and actress represented by IMG Models. == Modelling == She has worked for Elle, Vogue, and countless magazines and fashion shows & brands. As for Vogue, "When Vogue called me I couldn't believe it, it's every girl's dream to be on the cover, and there I was with five of the most beautiful girls in the world!!" == Other websites == * official website Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Indian actors Category:Indian models
title: Monikangana Dutta
